------------------------------------POST----------------------------------------------
1. Add Customer : Method "POST"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customers/addCustomer
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
   {
    "customerId" : 1,
    "customerName" : "ramesh",
    "customerEmail" : "ramesh@gmail.com",
    "username" : "ramesh",
    "password" : "ramesh"
	}
	
------------------------------------GET----------------------------------------------
1. Get Customer By Id : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customers/viewCustomer/id/4

1. Get All Customers : Method "GET"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customers/viewAllCustomers

------------------------------------UPDATE----------------------------------------------

1. Update Customer : Method "PUT"
2. URL: http://localhost:9092/customers/updateCustomer/id/4
3. INPUT: 
   Body -> Raw -> JSON
   {
    "customerId": 4,
    "customerName": "Smita Pradhan",
    "customerEmail": "smita123pradhan@gmail.com",
    "username": "smita",
    "password": "smita123",
    "address": null
	}
	
------------------------------------DELETE----------------------------------------------
1. Delete Customer : Method "DELETE"
2. URL:	http://localhost:9092/customers/deleteCustomer/id/12

